Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:38.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}此処に在るのが運命なら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:38.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\fs45\pos(459,981)}さだめ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:42.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}いっそぎゅっと　抱きしめて彼方まで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}-You must be here now-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:54.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}時空の旅人よ　瞼閉じて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:58.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}星屑を超えるスピードで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:02.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Dive into the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:06.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}物語の始まりまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:10.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}もがき　足掻き　続けていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:13.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ゼロから抜け出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼き時代を　信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\fs45\pos(201,982.5)}と  き
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:20.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Calling you Calling you Everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}謳え　叫べ　彷徨い人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:26.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}遥かな願いへと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:33.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}罪も　愛も　流して　go away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}魂ごと揺らせ揺らせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:40.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}命辿るHeralder
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:31.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}將流落到何處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:34.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}要追求何人而生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:38.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}如果命運要我留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:42.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}索性緊緊擁抱直至彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}-現在你必須在這裡-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:54.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}時空的旅人啊 閉上你的雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:58.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}用超越群星的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:02.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}潛入星海之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:06.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不斷翻滾 不停掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:10.15,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}直至故事的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:13.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}擺脫零的認識
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}相信蒼藍的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:20.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}呼喚你 在每一個角落呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}歌頌吧 吶喊吧 彷徨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:26.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}把所有的罪與所有的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:33.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}沖向遙遠的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}震撼整個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:40.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}追求生命的使者
